  "fixed_versions": [],
  "solution": "Upgrade your Splunk Docker image to the most up-to-date version using the image with the tag “latest”.\nDepending on your current image or container version, you can also upgrade using images with tags 10.2.2, 10.0.5, 9.4.10, 9.3.11, or higher.\nProduct Status\nProduct\nBase Version\nAffected Version\nFix Version\nsplunk/splunk\n10.2\n10.2.0 to 10.2.1\n10.2.2\nsplunk/splunk\n10.0\n10.0.0 to 10.0.4\n10.0.5\nsplunk/splunk\n9.4\n9.4.0 to 9.4.9\n9.4.10\nsplunk/splunk\n9.3\n9.3.0 to 9.3.10\n9.3.11",
